MESSENGER
v.
FINNEGAN 2018-1304 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 28, 2018 O'CONNOR, C.J., and O'DONNELL, FRENCH, FISCHER, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On S.Ct.Prac.R. 12.04 determination. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion to amend granted.

KENNEDY and DEWINE, JJ., would deny the petition on the merits.
